                        <interp inst="t18350202-name-205" type="given" value="JOHN FREDERICK"></interp>JOHN FREDERICK WITTOCK</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a merchant. On the 21st of January, I was on Ludgate-hill between four and five o'clock—I did not feel my handkerchief taken, but a young man told me of it, and I saw the prisoner secured—another person handed my handkerchief over to me—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
